metadata.name: Levitated Alien Signals
metadata.description:
Levitated Alien Signals is a community driven creation.
we took 5 polls to see which traits to include and this was the final outcome!

An ominous looking sentient being that is an overlooking figure of the Levitated Society. he is there to be with you throughout your minting experiences bringing you good luck on future investments.

Going to battle with rugs, have caused him to lose a limb in the process, but he is more than capable to see the future outcomes with his third eye
